# Tax Calculator Feature Tests — Implementation Plan

Complete feature test coverage for the Tax Calculator module, testing all controller routes and service logic using Pest PHP.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The [UserCalculationCountry](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/inertia/app/Models/UserCalculationCountry.php#8-44) model is missing `selected_tax_type_ids` and `tax_type_overrides` from both `$fillable` and `$casts`. The `TaxCalculatorService::saveStep2Data()` method writes to these fields, so they silently fail. This fix is required before tests will pass.

> [!WARNING]
> Tests will use `RefreshDatabase`, which **wipes the DB before each test**. Make sure you are not running these against a production database (standard Laravel practice).

---

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Model Fix — [UserCalculationCountry](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/inertia/app/Models/UserCalculationCountry.php#8-44)

#### [MODIFY] [UserCalculationCountry.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/inertia/app/Models/UserCalculationCountry.php)

Add `selected_tax_type_ids` and `tax_type_overrides` to `$fillable` and `$casts`:

```diff
 protected $fillable = [
     'user_calculation_id',
     'country_id',
     'days_spent',
     'is_tax_resident',
     'allocated_income',
     'taxable_income',
     'tax_due',
     'tax_by_type',
+    'selected_tax_type_ids',
+    'tax_type_overrides',
 ];

 protected $casts = [
     'is_tax_resident' => 'boolean',
     'tax_by_type'     => 'array',
+    'selected_tax_type_ids' => 'array',
+    'tax_type_overrides'    => 'array',
 ];
```

---

### 2. Model Factories (7 new files)

All factories go in `database/factories/`. We only have `UserFactory` currently.

| # | Factory File | Creates | Key Fields |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | [NEW] [CountryFactory.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/inertia/database/factories/CountryFactory.php) | `Country` | `name`, `iso_code`, `currency_code`, `tax_residency_days`, `flat_tax_rate`, `has_progressive_tax`, `is_active` |
| 2 | [NEW] [TaxTypeFactory.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/inertia/database/factories/TaxTypeFactory.php) | `TaxType` | `key`, `name`, `is_default`, `is_active`, `sort_order` |
| 3 | [NEW] [TaxBracketFactory.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/inertia/database/factories/TaxBracketFactory.php) | `TaxBracket` | `country_id`, `tax_type_id`, `tax_year`, `min_income`, `max_income`, `rate`, `is_active` |
| 4 | [NEW] [TaxTreatyFactory.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/inertia/database/factories/TaxTreatyFactory.php) | `TaxTreaty` | `country_a_id`, `country_b_id`, `treaty_type`, `applicable_tax_year`, `is_active` |
| 5 | [NEW] [UserCalculationFactory.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/inertia/database/factories/UserCalculationFactory.php) | `UserCalculation` | `session_uuid`, `gross_income`, `currency`, `country_id`, `citizenship_country_code`, `step_reached` |
| 6 | [NEW] [UserCalculationCountryFactory.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/inertia/database/factories/UserCalculationCountryFactory.php) | `UserCalculationCountry` | `user_calculation_id`, `country_id`, `days_spent`, `is_tax_resident` |
| 7 | [NEW] [SettingFactory.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/inertia/database/factories/SettingFactory.php) | `Setting` | `key`, `value`, `type` |

---

### 3. Feature Test Files (8 new files)

All tests in `tests/Feature/TaxCalculator/`. Uses **Pest PHP** syntax matching the existing test style.

---

#### [NEW] [TaxCalculatorStep1Test.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/inertia/tests/Feature/TaxCalculator/TaxCalculatorStep1Test.php)

**Tests the Step 1 controller routes: `GET /tax-calculator` and `POST /tax-calculator/step-1`**

| # | Test Case |
|---|---|
| 1 | `GET /tax-calculator` returns 200 with countries and currencies |
| 2 | `POST /step-1` with valid data creates `UserCalculation` and redirects to step-2 |
| 3 | `POST /step-1` with missing `annual_income` returns validation error |
| 4 | `POST /step-1` with invalid `currency` (not 3 chars) returns validation error |
| 5 | `POST /step-1` with non-existent `citizenship_country_id` returns validation error |
| 6 | `POST /step-1` twice with same session updates existing `UserCalculation` (not duplicate) |

---

#### [NEW] [TaxCalculatorStep2Test.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/inertia/tests/Feature/TaxCalculator/TaxCalculatorStep2Test.php)

**Tests the Step 2 controller routes: `GET /tax-calculator/step-2` and `POST /tax-calculator/step-2`**

| # | Test Case |
|---|---|
| 1 | `GET /step-2` redirects to index if no session UUID |
| 2 | `GET /step-2` renders correctly with valid session |
| 3 | `POST /step-2` stores residency periods and redirects to step-3 |
| 4 | `POST /step-2` fails if total days ≠ 365 |
| 5 | `POST /step-2` fails if days < 1 or > 365 |
| 6 | `POST /step-2` fails with duplicate country IDs |
| 7 | `POST /step-2` stores custom taxes correctly |
| 8 | `POST /step-2` redirects to index if session expired |

---

#### [NEW] [TaxCalculatorStep3Test.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/inertia/tests/Feature/TaxCalculator/TaxCalculatorStep3Test.php)

**Tests the Step 3 controller route: `GET /tax-calculator/step-3`**

| # | Test Case |
|---|---|
| 1 | `GET /step-3` redirects to index if no session |
| 2 | `GET /step-3` redirects to step-2 if no countries visited |
| 3 | `GET /step-3` renders result page with complete calculation data |
