## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests

Run the full test suite for the TaxCalculator module:

```bash
php artisan test --filter=TaxCalculator
```

Run individual test files to isolate failures:

```bash
php artisan test tests/Feature/TaxCalculator/TaxCalculatorStep1Test.php
php artisan test tests/Feature/TaxCalculator/TaxCalculationServiceTest.php
```

Expected: **All tests pass**, no existing test regressions.

### Regression Check

Run the full application test suite to ensure no regressions:

```bash
php artisan test
```
